# Title: Disabled Volume Snapshots
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-01-28
# Level: high
# Description: Detects commands that temporarily turn off Volume Snapshots
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_reg_volsnap_disable.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administration

CommandLine="*\\Services\\VSS\\Diag*" CommandLine="*/d Disabled*"